                            Add a free Alpha Vantage API key to see live prices with your analysis.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button onClick={() => setIsKeyModalOpen(true)} className="bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 flex-shrink-0">Enter API Key</button>
